616
00:31:20,220 --> 00:31:21,420
The impersonator's qualifications,

617
00:31:21,420 --> 00:31:22,700
school roll, educational background,

618
00:31:22,850 --> 00:31:23,500
and undergraduate degree

619
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,050
