620
00:31:24,570 --> 00:31:25,500
If they have a government post,

621
00:31:25,530 --> 00:31:26,460
they will be sacked.

622
00:31:26,850 --> 00:31:28,050
If they're employed,

623
00:31:28,090 --> 00:31:28,660
they might

624
00:31:28,770 --> 00:31:29,850
be sacked.

