It's actually very difficult

626
00:31:32,050 --> 00:31:33,290
for the victim

627
00:31:33,570 --> 00:31:35,130
to attend university again,

628
00:31:35,570 --> 00:31:36,850
especially for your case.

629
00:31:37,050 --> 00:31:38,530
It's been almost 10 years since the incident.

630
00:31:38,900 --> 00:31:40,260
It's impossible for the university

631
00:31:40,260 --> 00:31:41,980
to take you in
based on your results 10 years ago.

632
