653
00:32:31,500 --> 00:32:32,700
Qinglai will get back his land.

654
00:32:33,570 --> 00:32:34,660
Dad and Mom will get money in their pockets.

655
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,220
You can marry Yani

656
00:32:36,220 --> 00:32:38,020
