657
00:32:38,330 --> 00:32:39,020
Xiuyu,

658
00:32:39,020 --> 00:32:40,330
don't say that.

659
00:32:40,420 --> 00:32:41,770
I won't accept a single cent from them.

660
00:32:41,850 --> 00:32:42,660
You do make it sound nice.

661
00:32:43,290 --> 00:32:44,660
Do you really think that you don't need

662
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:45,850
to spend a single cent to marry Yani?

663
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:52,310
Xiuyu...

664
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:53,750
I thought you would be different

665
00:32:54,340 --> 00:32:56,340
since you attended university
and worked in the city.

666
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:59,140
I didn't expect you to be like the rest.

667
00:33:00,340 --> 00:33:01,180
You can go to work.

668
00:33:01,470 --> 00:33:02,180
I'm sorry.

669
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:03,270
Sorry for disturbing you.

670
00:33:03,900 --> 00:33:04,340
Xiuyu!

671
00:33:04,550 --> 00:33:05,420
Xiuyu!

672
00:33:05,620 --> 00:33:05,900
Xiuyu!

673
00:33:05,900 --> 00:33:06,860
Wait for me. I'm serious.

674
00:33:07,070 --> 00:33:08,030
I'll head to work now.

675
00:33:08,310 --> 00:33:09,070
Wait for me to come back.

676
00:33:09,070 --> 00:33:09,990
We can talk after that, okay?

677
00:33:10,100 --> 00:33:11,030
There's nothing for us to talk about.

678
00:33:11,950 --> 00:33:12,710
I'm sorry.

679
00:33:13,750 --> 00:33:15,030
I was unlucky

680
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:16,790
to be born in this family.

681
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:18,070
Xiuyu!

682
00:33:18,340 --> 00:33:18,990
Xiuyu!

683
00:33:19,230 --> 00:33:20,550
Xiuyu!

684
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:37,580
What?

685
