How could you guys do that?

686
00:33:40,860 --> 00:33:42,790
You even wanted them
to sign a confidentiality agreement?

687
00:33:43,340 --> 00:33:44,470
Anyway,

688
00:33:45,420 --> 00:33:46,420
I've already

689
00:33:46,710 --> 00:33:47,550
explained

690
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:49,750
the entire story to you.

691
00:33:50,270 --> 00:33:52,380
You're our legal consultant.

692
00:33:52,950 --> 00:33:54,420
This is your duty.

693
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:56,270
Just draft up an agreement
as soon as possible, okay?

694
00:33:56,470 --> 00:33:57,750
I'm the Group's legal consultant.

695
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:59,230
I'm not serving your family.

696
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:00,790
This is your family affair.

697
00:34:00,790 --> 00:34:02,180
I have the right to reject your request.

698
00:34:02,180 --> 00:34:03,230
Listen, Wan Chuanjia,

699
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,100
this matter...

700
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:05,860
I will never help you out.

701
00:34:05,860 --> 00:34:07,660
This is illegal, do you know that?

702
00:34:08,180 --> 00:34:10,100
How could you do such a dumb thing?

703
00:34:10,100 --> 00:34:11,580
That's an immoral thing for you to do!

704
00:34:11,580 --> 00:34:12,380
That's enough.

705
00:34:12,750 --> 00:34:14,030
Don't go overboard, okay?

706
00:34:15,380 --> 00:34:17,550
You don't have the right to lecture me.

707
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:20,140
We had a deal between us, right?

708
00:34:20,470 --> 00:34:22,830
If so, what gives you the right

709
00:34:23,030 --> 00:34:24,780
to lecture me like a saint?

710
00:34:30,510 --> 00:34:31,180
This issue

711
00:34:31,180 --> 00:34:32,260
can be big

712
00:34:32,430 --> 00:34:33,660
or small.

713
00:34:33,990 --> 00:34:35,510
It all depends on the words you use, right?

714
00:34:36,300 --> 00:34:37,780
They were the ones
who came up with the requests.

715
00:34:38,430 --> 00:34:39,780
We've already made a deal with them.

716
00:34:39,990 --> 00:34:41,740
We'll compensate them while they'll keep it a secret.
What's wrong with that?

717
00:34:43,390 --> 00:34:45,180
Every word I told you was true.

718
00:34:45,390 --> 00:34:47,100
If you don't believe me,
you can ask the Wang family.

719
00:34:50,430 --> 00:34:50,990
Fine.

720
00:34:52,140 --> 00:34:53,070
You guys are better than me.

721
00:34:54,660 --> 00:34:56,550
Please hire another legal expert to assist you.

722
00:34:56,990 --> 00:34:57,950
I've never learned how to draft up

723
00:34:57,950 --> 00:34:59,070
a contract with that many conditions in school.

724
00:34:59,620 --> 00:35:00,260
I don't know how to do it.

725
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:01,300
Xingyun!

726
00:35:10,870 --> 00:35:12,350
Look at your temper.

727
00:35:12,350 --> 00:35:14,030
You have such an explosive temper.

728
00:35:16,830 --> 00:35:17,510
You see,

729
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:19,220
two days ago,

730
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:21,070
we had a meal in the inn.

731
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:23,510
Although your sister

732
00:35:23,620 --> 00:35:24,470
clinched a deal with Xie

733
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:25,740
using an unorthodox method,

734
00:35:26,430 --> 00:35:27,660
I was planning to give you credits for it too.

735
00:35:29,180 --> 00:35:31,430
I was planning to let our group
extend our contract with your law firm.

736
00:35:32,140 --> 00:35:33,070
If you handle this,

737
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:34,740
not only will I extend our contract,

738
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:36,660
but I will also raise your agent fee rate

739
00:35:36,780 --> 00:35:38,390
from the standard 1%

740
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:40,550
to 5%, just like Han's rate.

741
00:35:42,470 --> 00:35:43,830
I'll extend our contract immediately
once you get this done.

742
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:45,740
But of course,

743
00:35:46,510 --> 00:35:47,550
if you're still unwilling

744
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:48,910
to draft up the contract

745
00:35:49,390 --> 00:35:50,260
after all I've said,

746
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:51,470
