747
00:35:52,100 --> 00:35:53,510
I can call Han immediately.

748
00:35:54,260 --> 00:35:55,070
With his capabilities,

749
00:35:55,070 --> 00:35:56,780
I'm sure he's better than you at this.

750
00:35:57,580 --> 00:35:59,140
If so, why didn't you go to him in the first place?

751
00:36:03,870 --> 00:36:04,990
After all,

752
00:36:06,350 --> 00:36:07,990
it's our family affair.

753
00:36:09,510 --> 00:36:10,950
We shouldn't wash our dirty linen in public.

754
00:36:11,580 --> 00:36:12,260
Besides,

755
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:13,830
if I do approach Han for this matter,

756
00:36:14,220 --> 00:36:15,390
should I look for you or him

757
00:36:15,780 --> 00:36:17,140
for the Group's legal matters

758
00:36:17,140 --> 00:36:18,350
if I do extend our contract with your law firm?

759
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:19,700
Am I right?

760
00:36:22,100 --> 00:36:22,990
Xingyun,

761
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:24,950
you're living in the city right now.

762
00:36:25,350 --> 00:36:26,350
