763
00:36:27,070 --> 00:36:29,390
Of course you know that it isn't that easy

764
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:31,830
to get a good job in the current society.

765
00:36:32,100 --> 00:36:33,780
Even if Xiuyu manages to attend university,

766
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:34,950
she still has to find a job

767
00:36:35,100 --> 00:36:36,180
after graduating from university, right?

768
00:36:37,430 --> 00:36:38,740
Can you promise that you'll find her a better job

769
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:39,950
than her current job?

770
00:36:40,660 --> 00:36:42,740
