781
00:37:01,990 --> 00:37:03,140
Xingyun, you're a smart girl.

782
00:37:03,140 --> 00:37:04,180
Think about it.

783
00:37:04,660 --> 00:37:05,740
Actually, we're just taking

784
00:37:06,220 --> 00:37:07,660
what we need from each other.

785
00:37:12,470 --> 00:37:14,550
Does Xingfu know about this?

786
00:37:14,870 --> 00:37:16,220
The Wang family isn't a bunch of idiots.

787
00:37:16,470 --> 00:37:17,580
Of course they won't let her know about this.

788
00:37:18,510 --> 00:37:19,620
In their hearts,

789
00:37:19,620 --> 00:37:21,510
your sister will always be an outsider.

790
00:37:21,870 --> 00:37:22,620
Wang Qinglai,

791
00:37:22,910 --> 00:37:23,910
your so-called brother-in-law,

792
00:37:24,220 --> 00:37:26,660
didn't even dare to tell your sister about this.

793
00:37:29,580 --> 00:37:30,180
So,

794
00:37:30,780 --> 00:37:32,030
