808
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:04,620
And,

809
00:38:06,430 --> 00:38:08,180
if I do approach Han,

810
00:38:09,140 --> 00:38:10,260
I'm sure you know

811
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:11,350
his personality better than I do.

812
00:38:12,140 --> 00:38:13,780
He's greedier

813
00:38:13,870 --> 00:38:15,030
and more ruthless than you.

814
00:38:15,260 --> 00:38:16,660
That's why I would rather

815
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:17,780
let you have the goods on us

816
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:20,220
than enlist his service.

817
00:38:24,390 --> 00:38:25,470
After all,

818
00:38:25,470 --> 00:38:27,260
I still treat you as a part of the family.

819
00:38:29,830 --> 00:38:30,620
Wan Chuanjia,

820
00:38:30,990 --> 00:38:31,910
from now on,

821
00:38:33,180 --> 00:38:34,350
no matter if it's my sister's inn

822
00:38:34,390 --> 00:38:35,300
