824
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:40,260
Deal.

825
00:38:41,780 --> 00:38:42,430
Is there anything else?

826
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:43,780
It's fine. Take your time.

827
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:45,430
You can think about it slowly.

828
00:38:45,780 --> 00:38:46,950
Tell me

829
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:48,030
if you have any other ideas.

830
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:49,260
