831
00:38:49,830 --> 00:38:51,660
People are successful for certain reasons.

832
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:53,470
Look at how intelligent you are. Good for you.

833
00:38:57,390 --> 00:38:58,830
I'll send it to your email once I'm done.

834
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:00,100
I appreciate your effort.

835
00:39:06,300 --> 00:39:07,220
Wan Chuanjia,

836
00:39:07,990 --> 00:39:09,910
do not ever tell my sister about this.

837
00:39:11,780 --> 00:39:12,220
Of course.

838
00:39:21,620 --> 00:39:22,260
Hello?

839
00:39:22,510 --> 00:39:23,780
