842
00:39:28,100 --> 00:39:29,220
I'm really sorry about this.

843
00:39:29,220 --> 00:39:30,300
We ran out of rooms.

844
00:39:30,300 --> 00:39:31,700
Call me if you have any rooms available.

845
00:39:32,220 --> 00:39:33,700
